This paper is primarily focused on the detection of malicious Android applications using machine learning models. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning models, which suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses the interpretability of decisions made by the machine learning models, which could place it in cs.SE (Software Engineering) or cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
